# snippets with placeholder tokens: REDACTED_HOST, REDACTED_DROPLET,
# REDACTED_PID. Those are historical artifacts from the private twin, not
# runtime config — no env var maps to them. Leave them alone unless you're
# rewriting the docs for a public audience.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
